<div class="index-c1 w1200">
    <div class="index-tlt1">
        <h2>关于我们</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="c1-con clearfix">
        <div class="c1-left wow fadeInLeft animated">
            <img src="https://www.zkcx.com/data/upload/202008/20200813112809_449.jpg" />
        </div>
        <div class="c1-right wow fadeInUp animated">
            <h3>武汉中科创新技术股份有限公司</h3>
